message.body: Wednesday will be good for this week! Will you be doing your shift next week?
Nope! Just this week. We can meet tho
So someone else will be there next week? Any chance it's a psych person like you!
I was checking bc I wanted to see if we could meet once for each paper. But ill make another apt and oh yeah they should change that!

I'm the only psych person. Someone will be there if I can get someone to cover for me...if not then no but you can make an appt with anyone else that week (and I think there are Wednesday evening spots still open)
I agree! And like I said I can still meet with you sometime that week
Yeah so once this Wednesday and once sometime next week
Sweet , I can do whenever next week
